ntour features that include more global (i.e. large-range) contexts, includ=
ing curvature, connectivity, etc.<br><br>The overall method is illustrated =
in Figure 3, which involves the following preprocessing works in the master=
 branch:<br>(1) arrange multiple layers of satellite chains (a list of view=
points) over the target object; and<br>(2) create the Eigen-Graph [Xu, Zhou=
, and Qiao 2020] to obtain the eigenvalue features; <br>(3) employ three T-=
