ransform the N point coordinates for the Local and Global Representation Br=
anches and the last one to output multiple 3x3 matrices to transform the sa=
tellite chains.<br><br>After that, the method employs the Global and Local =
Representation Branches:<br>(1) the local representation branch stacks two =
Space Convolution layers to hierarchically extract the local information, f=
ollowed by an FC layer; and<br>(2) the global representation branch include=
s the satellite chain module (to observe the point cloud over a chain of vi=
ewpoints), Satellite Encoding Module (to capture the geometric relationship=
