nt Module (to explore relative point positions).<br><br>Finally, the method=
 concatenates the outputs of the Local and Global Representation Branches a=
s the final representation of the input point cloud for classification via =
a Multi-Layer Perceptron.<br><br>Overall the technical contribution is a fr=
